io.permazen.core.type

Class PatternType

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.permazen.core.FieldType<T>
      • io.permazen.core.type.NullSafeType<T>
        • io.permazen.core.type.StringEncodedType<Pattern>
          • io.permazen.core.type.PatternType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparator<Pattern>

    public class PatternType
extends StringEncodedType<Pattern>
    Pattern type. Null values are supported by this class.

    Note: equality is defined by equal pattern strings, which is not consistent with the method Pattern.equals(), which is not implemented and therefore defaults to object identity for comparision.
